text:
Hello beautiful people <!channel>

Hope you’re having a great day!!

Just a quick reminder for Saturday June 24 at Southern Bell  with <@U02MANZL55F>!!!
It’s going to be a blast and tasty without regrets! :arrow_up: vote above if you haven’t.

Second far away reminder is a hike with Zvi towards late August/ early September.
With a cabin getaway as well around that same time period. :hut:

Two quick comments:
1. Anybody going to be in Barcelona, Spain on June 29th? There’s a CoC event happening there and we’re looking for people. 
2. If you haven’t already joined this LinkedIn Group, feel free to and be connected to events with CoC/Alumni/Colleen who you might have met at OMSCS Conference: <https://www.linkedin.com/groups/884/>
That’s all for now!! Only a few people for the online games so I’m going to give ya’ll a breather from me in June.

For fun discussion to reply to this thread, _*what classes are people taking in the fall*_???
Because registration is happening next week!!! Find your friends or study buddies!

Have fun and keep pushing for those in summer classes!! :muscle:
Cherie Lum
